                            "alt": "2.0",
                            "game-obj": "Sources",
                            "aonid": 216
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "8b30b9256178684bb3d817f553b1b33c",
                "text": "A general feat with the skill trait improves your skills and their actions or gives you new actions for a skill. A feat with this trait can be selected when a class grants a skill feat or general feat. Archetype feats with the skill trait can be selected in place of a skill feat if you have that archetype\u2019s dedication feat."
            }
        ],
        "prerequisite": "legendary in *Intimidation*",
        "critical_success": "The target must attempt a Fortitude save against your Intimidation DC. On a critical failure, it dies. On any other result, it becomes frightened 2 and is fleeing for 1 round. The critical failure effect has the death trait.",
        "success": "The target becomes frightened 2.",
        "failure": "The target becomes frightened 1.",
